Love this place!! Best bowl of Pho in the city, if you ask me. The service is always quick and price is a great value. The interior is a little institutional in nature, for a churn and burn pace, but delicious food, quick service and a huge menu give it the edge that the ambiance lacks. When food is stellar, a hole in the wall spot can slide on the less important details.

